A user’s license is not required for a person who uses fuel in a motor vehicle
on which an emblem issued for the motor vehicle pursuant to ORS 319.535 is
displayed. [Amended by 1959 c.188 s3; 1977 c.429 s2; 1985 c.265 s1; 1989 c.992 s25;
